### Verb signatures used (all real, no invented verbs)
  http/serve, cortex/*, artifact/*, audio/listen, time/now, llm/* (to local),
  eval, display — all in CORE.

### Pair-yield estimate
  From graph-of-do-and-dont/motoi-subsystem-limits.slat (14 nodes × 12 templates):
    ~1,200 pairs (largest single yield in this plan)
  From book-of-computing/08 extend:  ~150 pairs
  From book-of-systems/02 extend:    ~400 pairs (systematic walkthrough)
  From book-of-scheme/appendix-G:    ~80 pairs
  From book-of-introspection/16.12:  ~120 pairs
